## [config.version] - Preview 10
- Reimagined and added back the Debbie leaning on the counter scene.

- Rebuilt Debbie's progressive shower events and added to cookie jar.

- Added the repeatable version of getting caught with Debbie's pants.

- Developed capability to prevent unwanted visitors to Anon's bedroom.
- Inadvertently caused playtest team to found _The Cult of the Chair_.

- Split out Maria's hair flower so it can be oriented correctly.
- Established the base for Maria's button dialogue options.
- Updated the repairing Debbie's car quest to support visiting Josie in person.
- Installed basic functionality for the car dealership.
- Improved Josephine face art, especially lighting of her teeth.
- Hooked up buttons and schedules for the various dealership employees.
- Published "Muffdiver" magazine and allowed it to be viewed in the inventory.
- Implemented easy difficulty to automatically skip some mini games.
- Changed the tutorial to only trigger if it has already been seen.
- Restaged Debbie's kitchen dialogue to better reflect button position.
- Touched up art for some of the pizzeria and dealership locations.
- Finished removing old Anon art from Jenny's photo quest.
- Tweaked a couple of Debbie quest reminders to not block her button.
- Addressed Jenny referencing payment that may never have occurred.
- Stopped Debbie trying to cook during the helping around the house quest.
- Ensured Anon eventually gets wet when showering with Jenny.
- Optimised rig attribute preprocessing and added a feature to aid organisation.
- Made it much easier to share sets of assets between rig poses.
- Fixed soft-lock in Debbie pool quest to when Jenny was using the bathroom.
- Prevented bad player state after first Jenny telescope quest.
- Repaired posing for Debbie drying her breasts just outside the shower.
- Cleaned up scene previews that may now be unlocked normally.
- Upgraded Ren'Py to version 8.5.0.
- Various metadata additions, typo fixes, and consistency tweaks.

- Fixed save migrations for saves made prior to 21.0.0-wip.5252.
- Added missing dialogue arm asset for Debbie while pregnant.

- Fixed Jenny becoming invisible in cam show videos while pregnant.

- Resolved conflict between Miss Dewitt and Miss Ross routes when collecting planks.
- Ensured replay of Debbie blowjob scene in Anon's room correctly unlocks.
- Applied correct tint to Anon's bedsheets during Debbie's visits.
- Attempted to support two-decade old hardware in equirectangular projection shader.
- Upgraded Ren'Py to version 8.4.1, and made new accessibility options available.

- Added one original, one reworked, and one upgraded quest to Debbie's route.
- Continued the main story with two more upgraded quests and pizza mini game.
- Expanded Debbie's recurring shower event with another level of escalation.
- Included two new animations, for future quests, in shower previews section.
- Made previewable animations available, already unlocked, to the cookie jar.
- Moved rig system over to new positioning system.
- Overhauled how transitions are managed to better facilitate future usage.
- Drew many more art assets for Anon, Debbie, Dimitri, Igor, and Kassy.
- Revisited Jenny cam show handjob animation and added more frames.
- Enhanced Jenny shower blowjob scene with more cum frames and other tweaks.
- Worked on adding variety to Summerville in the form of More crowd variants.
- Reworked washroom and second floor concourse of the mall with more details.
- Created art for a new TV show for use in Debbie's route.
- Extended the Cupid store location with a new storage room.
- Plumbed in the next stage of Debbie's pool button.
- Installed water VFX for shower preview animation.
- Fixed part of Jenny's initial sex camshow quest being accidentally skipped.
- Tweaked second dream sequence in Debbie's route to be more performant.
- Allowed photo booth to be interacted with once again.
- Prevented minor state corruption when clearing the shower at night.
- Guarded against pathological player behaviour in Roxxy visit quest.
- Various minor posing improvements.
## 21.0.0-wip.5791 - Preview 6, Hotfix 1
- Fixed crash in Debbie's mall trip event if Anon was busy the night prior.
- Corrected minor typo in reminder dialogue for Debbie's mall trip event.
- Continued Debbie's route with one original, two reworked, and two upgraded quests.
- Added another level of escalation into Debbie's recurring shower event.
- Allowed three new animations, intended for future quests, to be previewed early.
- Restored the first two quests of Diane's route, including gardening mini game.
- Wired up Diane's early game button in her garden.
- Overhauled a large number of assets and scenes that occur on Debbie's couch.
- Expanded the forest slightly. Don't worry about it, nothing see there. >_>;;
- Created a new blend mode to help simulate dimming of light sources.
- Combined some cutscene assets, allowing art to be upgraded while saving space.
- Slowed speed of vertical pan the first time Anon dreams of Debbie.
- Mitigated issue impacting cancellation of auto-nav in deferred events.
- Adjusted some character information in the contacts app, and added Diane.
- Spaced out the timeline between a couple of existing Debbie quests.
- Made a minor cutscene variation for the lotion variant of Deb's Mall event.
- Applied patch to prevent incorrect rendering of some visual effects on Android.

- Fixed incorrect zoning of Diane's house which could break some quests.
- Resolved a soft-lock in Miss Okita's route concerning Mrs. Smith's office.

- Improved text layout of background information in contacts app.
- Corrected various typos in existing dialogue.
## 21.0.0-wip.5605 - Preview 5, Hotfix 2
- Increased resolution of assets used in Anon's nightmare.
- Fixed Jenny not always rendering correctly during Anon's nightmare.
- Restored translation support in choice menus.
- Hid duplicate Debbie that could appear in background of a few scenes.

- Fixed Debbie not always rendering correctly during Anon's panty flashback.
- Expanded Debbie's route with one original, three reworked, and six upgraded quests.
- Created a new mall trip event with Debbie that evolves with her story.
- Moved over to using Debbie's new art when she appears in other routes.
- Updated Debbie's art in her button dialogue, including sleeping Debbie.
- Rebuilt peeking on Debbie in the shower event with more new art.

- Built new x-ray system and began adding it to existing scenes.
- Wrote up Frank and Bridget's background information for the phone.
- Improved dialogue hint when clicking on exterior garage door with key.
- Locked that lotion bottle in Debbie's drawer. For now.
- Restored correct hover effect to quick menu.
- Prevented quick load feature attempting to load incompatible saves.
- Removed non-functional options from quick menu when viewing a replay.
- Revisited animation system to improve stability, most notably during rollback.

- Fixed edge-case migration issue when loading some saves from Preview 1.

- Various small posing improvements to Debbie content from last preview.
- Ensured consistent view of hallway in Debbie's house during navigation.
- Adjusted timings of some ambient sounds to avoid hard cuts as they loop.
- Addressed issue where map music could linger into rails dialogue.
- Dealt with flip-flop continuity issues in Jenny's telescope scenes.
- Made sure the fake guitar is added to the wall properly in Melody's route.
- Cobbled together a new shader to support equirectangular projection.
- Optimised some hot code paths to keep navigation snappy.
- Resolved issue where using spot metadata would prevent asset prediction.
- Added a basic bloom visual effect to help distinguish daydreams.
- Helped rails to feel a little more natural when multiple paths may be taken.
- Enabled visible cues for choices that require unmet stat checks.
- Developed many new rig assets for both Jiang and Kassy.

- Touched up art of Anon using telescope in Jenny's route.

- Produced new assets for Jenny to reflect her pregnancy in Debbie's route.
- Revamped various cutscenes and created multiple new ones.
- Put together a new translatable module to help with expressing time periods.

- Integrated meeting Tammy outside Debbie's house with new mall trip event.
- Found and fixed a latent bug in how metadata scaling was being applied.
- Solved problem that would cause some sounds to play sooner than intended.

- Stopped Jenny's first sex toy quest from interfering with the timeline.
- Remedied various issues when Jenny showered at night.
- Introduced small dialogue variations to account for when Deb is at the mall.
- Inserted variant for claiming glasses from Judith during art class.
- Many small asset changes to adjust expressions and smooth arm joints.
- Reduced the use of magic numbers throughout the priority system.

- Eliminated various other minor bugs in existing quests.

- Resolved Debbie's route failing to re-activate correctly in some migrated saves.
- Fixed soft-lock in Judith's locker when reclaiming library book from Camila.
- Added all new event early in Debbie's story.
- Upgraded four of Debbie's existing quests with new art and dialogue.
- Improved existing cutscenes and added new ones.
- Updated home location backgrounds and closeups.
